Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【制作名单】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}片源提供:{\fscx90}Zhq
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}对白翻译:呆呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}对白校对:灰 Edge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}繁体校正:空心之人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}字幕计时:斌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}后期制作:{\fscx90}MR Yaha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}资料制作:大吉 灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.53,staff2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}bbs.dmhy.net
